replies.body:
I used to play exclusively ARAM until recently, I decided I wanted to get some mastery on champs. All that ARAM really put me out of practice for SR. 
I don't quite understand the lack of mastery on ARAM. Doesn't make much sense to me- you're still playing the champion, you're still improving with them. I can understand if it gives you less mastery, because of the lack of SR experience, but still.

Out of curiousity, has anybody received a key fragment in ARAM yet? I only play SR with friends and one of them (bless them) carried me with an S rank to get my second chest, and I want to earn keys but alas... I read in the Q&A that they'd drop in ARAM but I haven't gotten one yet ;o;
